aus mnu`K dw nwm AslI (ArQW ivc) 'rwmdwsu' (pRBU dw syvk) hY;
aus nUM srb-ivAwpI pRBU id`s pYNdw hY,
dwsW dw dws hox dy suBwau nwl aus ny pRBU nUM l`Bw hY[
jo (mnu`K) sdw pRBU nUM nyVy jwxdw hY,
auh syvk drgwh ivc kbUl huMdw hY[
pRBU aus syvk auqy Awp myhr krdw hY,
qy aus syvk nUM swrI smJ Aw jWdI hY[
swry prvwr ivc (rihMdw hoieAw BI) auh AMdroN inrmoh huMdw hY;
hy nwnk! ieho ijhI (jIvn-) jugqI nwl auh (AslI) "rwmdws" (rwm dw dws bx jWdw hY) ]6]
jo mnu`K pRBU dI rzw nUM mn ivc im`TI kr ky mMndw hY,
auhI jIaUNdw mukq AKvwauNdw hY;
aus nUM ^uSI qy ZmI ieko ijhI hY,
aus nUM sdw AwnMd hY (ikauNik) EQy (Bwv, aus dy ihrdy ivc pRBU-crnW qoN) ivCoVw nhIN hY[
sonw qy im`tI (BI aus mnu`K vwsqy) brwbr hY (Bwv, sonw vyK ky auh loB ivc nhIN Psdw),
AMimRq qy kauVI ivhu BI aus leI iek jYsI hY[
(iksy vloN) Awdr (dw vrqwau hovy) jW AhMkwr (dw) (aus mnu`K vwsqy) iek smwn hY,
kMgwl qy ShnSwh BI aus dI nzr ivc brwbr hY[
jo (rzw pRBU) vrqwauNdw hY, auhI (aus vwsqy) izMdgI dw gwfI-rwh hY;
hy nwnk! auh mnu`K jIaUNdw mukq ikhw jw skdw hY ]7]
swry QW (srIr-rUp Gr) Akwl purK dy hI hn,
ijs ijs QW jIvW nUM r`Kdw hY, auho ijhw auhnW dw nwauN (pY jWdw hY)[
pRBU Awp hI (sB kuJ) krn dI (qy jIvW pwsoN) krwaux dI qwkq r`Kdw hY,
jo pRBU nUM cMgw l`gdw hY auhI huMdw hY[
(izMdgI dIAW) byAMq lihrW bx ky (Akwl purK) Awp sB QweIN mOjUd hY,
Akwl purK dy Kyl ibAwn nhIN kIqy jw skdy[
ijho ijhI Akl dyNdw hY, auho ijhw zhUr (jIv dy AMdr) huMdw hY;
Akwl purK (Awp sB kuJ) krn vwlw hY qy kdy mrdw nhIN[
pRBU sdw myhr krn vwlw hY,
hy nwnk! (jIv aus nUM) sdw ismr ky (Pu`l vWg) iKVy rihMdy hn ]8]9]
